## API Contracts

Base URL: /api/v1
Auth: {% if tech_profile.needs_auth %}Bearer token (Supabase JWT) in Authorization header{% else %}None required{% endif %}

{% for feature in features %}
### {{ feature.name }} Endpoints

POST /{{ feature.id }}
  Body: { /* {{ feature.name }} fields */ }
  Returns: { id, created_at, /* fields */ }
  Auth required: {{ "yes" if tech_profile.needs_auth else "no" }}

GET /{{ feature.id }}
  Returns: Array of {{ feature.name }} objects
  Supports: ?limit=20&offset=0&sort=created_at

GET /{{ feature.id }}/:id
  Returns: Single {{ feature.name }} object
  Errors: 404 if not found, 403 if not owner

PUT /{{ feature.id }}/:id
  Body: Partial {{ feature.name }} fields
  Returns: Updated object

DELETE /{{ feature.id }}/:id
  Returns: 204 No Content

{% endfor %}
